6. What happens behind the scenes

Even though users click buttons, the system automatically:

Creates accounts
Assigns permissions
Sends notifications
Checks rules
Logs everything
Removes access during exit
7. Key concept: Automation

Instead of humans doing repetitive work:

Manual Work ❌	Automated System ✔
Email IT for account	Auto account creation
Track onboarding manually	System tracks progress
Remember exit steps	Auto access removal
8. Key concept: Safety

The system is designed to prevent mistakes:

No duplicate employees
No unauthorized access
No forgotten accounts after exit
Every action is logged
9. One-line summary

👉 This system ensures every employee is automatically onboarded, managed, and offboarded safely without manual effort or security gaps.

10. Simple real-life analogy

Think of it like a smart airport system:

Ticket booked → system prepares everything
Passenger arrives → all gates open automatically
Flight ends → system safely clears everything
